verses.text: Calec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová. Co b'itejec ak' b'it t'a Jehová. Co b'itejec b'it t'ay b'aj molan onh ek' a onh yic onhxo tik.
Ex vetisraelal, conh tzalajec yet' co Diosal chaannaquel yich co nación tik. Conh tzalajec yet' co Reyal a onh aj chonhab' Sion onh tik.
Conh q'ueec cheneljoc scalanec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová, yic scak'an ejmelal t'ay. Conh b'itanec t'ay yet' te' arpa yet' pandereta,
yujto stzalaj qued'oc a onh schonhab' onh tik. Ol yak' co tzalajk'olal a onh emnaquil onh tik, yujto ol yak' co colnab'il.
Yuj snivanil yelk'och Jehová, conh tzalajec a onh yic onhxo tik. Anhejtona' conh b'itanec t'ay yuj tzalajk'olal ayic tzonh vaycan ochi.
Q'ueocab' cav co b'itan d'ha Dios, haxo jun q'uen espada ay ye t'a schab'il pak'anh yamb'il cuuj,
yic scak'anek' co pac t'a eb' ch'oc chonhab'il, scak'anoch yaelal t'a juntzanh nación,
yic wach' tz'och q'uen cadena t'a sreyal eb' yet' t'a eb' anima ay yopisio t'a skal eb',
yic scotcan yaelal t'a yib'anh eb', aton tz'ib'yajcani. Ha jun niwan opisio tik syak' Dios t'a masanil eb' sk'anab'ajan t'ay. Calec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová.
